{"tid":2391013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特首稱與終審法院首席法官會面正常 雙方無討論案件","createTime":"2021-02-02T02:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T04:32:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a8592bdd226b7bb3c5d0be8041750e2bbc9ba2","tid":2391013,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/152129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F152129&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b1053337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/152129</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥強調，與現任或前任終審法院首席法官會面是合法、適當及正常，不應被解讀為干預司法獨立，並指這說法是不能接受，任何行政長官也不會這樣做，強調雙方會面從沒有討論到任何案件。 林鄭月娥在行政會議前被問到，她上周曾與首席法官張舉能單獨會面，而終審法院則將處理壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英涉案的保釋聆訊。林鄭月娥強調，要明確指出作為特區政府的行政長官，有義務維護司法獨立，這也是《基本法》列明的法定職責。她說有需要與首席法官會面，討論有關司法獨立、司法機構的效率及運作等事宜，反問若雙方不會面，如何討論有關議題。<br />\n<br />\n2021-02-02 10:48:26"},{"pid":"a62dbb3e6c1eecfa3039b4d2cc958ee1673de5ab","tid":2391013,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"瘋了，瘋了，都已經瘋了。"},{"pid":"fc6de9cb45128a7f3556cf2a426e6167765bde16","tid":2391013,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"冇討論案件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef7c153449dd88006d72dae5386d1d924ec377f","tid":2391013,"uid":5523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"打狗! 往死裡打!!"},{"pid":"55e1e49d0e731de6ec5875357fc0978e4d5cd4ad","tid":2391013,"uid":26014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"正常特首可以同法官討論案件?"},{"pid":"2499447f4ed48d2f542771a45566537ea0ed2cdd","tid":2391013,"uid":39221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02